---
title: Hawaiian-Style Coconut Tempura Shrimp with Tropical Slaw, Zesty Rice & Sweet ’n’ Spicy Sauce
description: There’s not much better than the light and airy crunch of something tempura-fried. We added toasted coconut to this magical Japanese-style batter, then coated and quick-fried shrimp for a sweet and savory bite. The crispy shrimp are piled over lime rice and served with a tropical slaw for a Hawaiian-inspired twist just in time for Asian Heritage Month! Everything is drizzled with a sweet-spicy-tangy sauce. What are you waiting for?!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/660c5b5f9149ba03ec9b05e2-8d71a930.jpeg
